---
title: Creamy Turkey Masala with Veggie Packed Rice
description: Move aside take-away curry temptations, step in Mimi’s masala. Mimi’s given everyone’s favourite curry recipe a flavour twist, using super-lean turkey steaks instead of chicken to add a depth of flavour that works perfectly with the creamy, tomato-rich sauce. Bursting with fresh flavours, ready in 30 minutes, and containing 4 of your 5 a day, we’re pretty sure this curry is about to become a household favourite.
